                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question"><div class="faq-icon">Q</div>What's the difference between 3-tab and architectural shingles?</div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">Architectural shingles are dimensional — thicker, heavier, and layered. They carry 30-year warranties and handle Michigan wind and hail better. Most homeowners choosing a replacement today go architectural for the longer return on investment.</div>
